data.description: Come home to convenience! Motivated seller! This home is located in a beautiful neighborhood near award-winning Richland 2 schools and minutes away from Sandhills, Ft Jackson, NE shopping, and the interstates. It features a dedicated office, three additional bedrooms, and a raised bed garden. The kitchen has granite countertops, touch-on water faucets, crown molding cabinets, a pantry, a breakfast bar, and a separate eating area. The open floor plan allows for easy conversation while cooking. Sliding glass doors open to the fenced yard. The owner's suite is enormous, and the secondary bedrooms share a hall bath. The home also includes a transferable termite bond, keyless front entry, and current appliances. The garage is finished and comes with a garage door opener. Guest parking is available directly across the street. Send your best offer!
